---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy — CalcKaro" description="Privacy Policy for CalcKaro, detailing our data practices.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6 py-8 text-xs leading-relaxed text-ink-muted">
    <div class="border-b border-vercel-gray-medium pb-4">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-2">Last updated: June 2026</p>
    </div>

    <p>
      At CalcKaro, accessible from calckaro.com, one of our main priorities is the privacy of our visitors. This Privacy Policy document contains types of information that is collected and recorded by CalcKaro and how we use it.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-white mt-6">Consent</h2>
    <p>By using our website, you hereby consent to our Privacy Policy and agree to its terms.</p>

    <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-white mt-6">Information We (Don't) Collect</h2>
    <p>
      CalcKaro is a client-side utility hub. **We do not collect, store, or transmit any inputs or numbers you enter into our calculators.** All calculations are executed directly in your browser. 
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-white mt-6">Log Files & Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      CalcKaro follows a standard procedure of using log files. These files log visitors when they visit websites. The information collected by log files includes internet protocol (IP) addresses, browser type, Internet Service Provider (ISP), date/time stamp, and referring/exit pages. These are not linked to any information that is personally identifiable.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-white mt-6">Google DoubleClick DART Cookie</h2>
    <p>
      Google is one of the third-party vendors on our site. It uses cookies, known as DART cookies, to serve ads to our site visitors based upon their visit to calckaro.com and other sites on the internet. Visitors may choose to decline the use of DART cookies by visiting the Google ad and content network Privacy Policy.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
